From 6d86e013f4fd4a831cc4906aca92224fc58a8232 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: CJ Damsleth <kim@damsleth.no>
Date: Thu, 23 Jul 2026 23:38:39 +0200
Subject: [RFC PATCH v1 2/4] arm64: dts: apple: add T6040 and J614s MacBook Pro

Add the common T6040 SoC description and the J614s board.  The topology
describes the 14 active cores reported by this M4 Pro SKU.  It retains the
disabled positional CPU slot so affinity numbering stays accurate.

The PMGR domain corpus is derived from the J614s ADT.  Raw-boot-only policy
properties are intentionally omitted; platform quirks belong in the driver.

Signed-off-by: CJ Damsleth <kim@damsleth.no>
---
